{"tid":332470,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"亞洲地區便利店排行榜","createTime":"2017-07-23T04:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T19:45:38.000Z","uid":60015,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"00da6ee49b1b4c0746f1e052e878c4dc4e3523c6","tid":332470,"uid":60015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T04:23:55.000Z","msg":"細佬我見識少去過嘅地方都少<br />\n淨係去過中 日 韓 台 港<br />\n但我去親旅行都好鐘意行佢地嘅便利店掃貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我心目中嘅排名係<br />\n1.日本<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/121207_3c6a7407561d5d47e65df90c26591e1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F121207_3c6a7407561d5d47e65df90c26591e1b.jpg&h=b7249de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n包羅萬有<br />\n乜撚都有得賣<br />\n便當熟食種類又多 仲要好食<br />\n零食 飲品種類更加係唔洗多講 要乜有乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除咗食物飲品之外仲有好多唔同種類嘅商品<br />\n仲要好多裝修都靚 坐得舒服<br />\n<br />\n2.台灣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/122333_ee9342bc5e31b933c4e654e1c2884184.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F122333_ee9342bc5e31b933c4e654e1c2884184.jpg&h=293916b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣便利店嘅食物種類都好多<br />\n而且好食<br />\n密度都好高 每幾步有一間<br />\n但係多數都係素化黑心食品<br />\n而且啲裝修通常都柒<br />\n坐得唔多舒服<br />\n部份便利店都幾撚污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後嗰啲陣間再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7060ffad23528c8dd0f27bba6828f23dd00fedf3","tid":332470,"uid":60015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T04:25:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2dcd2f0549d1abb1c24d6cfa039ad30c11d51b0","tid":332470,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T04:25:57.000Z","msg":"日本真係世界級"},{"pid":